       <span class="mi">j</span>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
    <span xlink:href="41467_2019_11720_Article_IEq11.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   </div>
  </div> are the autocorrelations of the sampled time series 
  <span class="italic">X</span> and 
  <span class="italic">Y</span> at time lag 
  <span class="italic">j</span>, respectively.
 </p>
